Itu Presiden Yamazaki!

92
00:07:27,971 --> 00:07:30,171
Panggil polisi dan dokter!

93
00:07:30,171 --> 00:07:31,071
Baik!

94
00:07:43,471 --> 00:07:44,571
Sebuah balon?

95
00:07:56,971 --> 00:07:59,071
Semprotan insektisida?

96
00:08:02,471 --> 00:08:03,771
Terlambat.

97
00:08:18,071 --> 00:08:19,571
Nyonya!

98
00:08:21,071 --> 00:08:22,571
Ini buruk.

99
00:08:23,771 --> 00:08:27,371
